*1996年纪录片《亨利·米勒还活着》（''Henry Miller Is Not Dead''），音乐由{{link-en|劳里·安德森|Laurie Anderson}}负责<ref>{{cite web|url= http://movingimages.ca/store/products.php?henry_miller|title= Henry Miller Is Not Dead|accessdate= 2011-09-26|publisher= Moving Images Distribution Society|archive-date= 2012-03-07|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120307025506/http://movingimages.ca/store/products.php?henry_miller|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

